node.text:
Nerf secret mission!

In part 1 of this inspirational mission with @nerf, we introduce the first two kids in this series. We are able to make a girl named Zahara's dream come true and inspired her to help another kid realize his dream too. You don't want to miss these beautiful moments. Part 2 drops tomorrow.

node.text: Julian Edelman vs. Guy Fieri, the Nerf battle you never saw coming! Normally Julian’s making clutch catches, but he’s also been known to launch a few darts 🎯 Parents, check out our story for where to buy the new Nerf Elite 2.0 Commander and Turbine. Who’s seen @skybrown, @diplo, @KlayThompson, and @GuyFieri’s Nerf House collabs?!
